==Useful Info==
'''Wendigos''' are found in [[Cocytus]]. Their signature ability is turning nearby [[simulacra]] into blasts of ice, dealing heavy damage. Their secondary spell lets them paralyze you for one turn and deal damage, possibly to blast you with an additional [[seracfall]].
{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*[[Paralysis]] for even a single turn can be deadly, especially if there is a group of monsters nearby.
*[[Seracfall]]s do extreme damage, partially bypass cold resistance and completely ignore your EV score. Wendigos cannot use this lethal spell if no [[simulacrum (monster)|simulacra]] are in your line of sight, so make generous use of [[Ignition]] or other area-of-effect spells to ensure they never share the same screen.

==History==
Wendigos were added in [[0.28]].
